                    "locale": {
                        "el-gr": {
                            "display_title": "Καλλιστεία Σκύλων της Χάρτλεϊκ Σίτυ",
                            "description": "Αυτή είναι μια φανταστική μέρα για τα όμορφα κουταβάκια της Χάρτλεϊκ Σίτυ! Η Μία θα πάει τα δύο κουταβάκια της στα ετήσια καλλιστεία σκύλων της Χάρτλεϊκ Σίτυ. Βοήθησέ την να τα επιδείξει πάνω στο βάθρο και  στον διάδρομο για τους κριτές! Μετά, καθοδήγησέ τα μέσα από το δρόμο μετ’ εμποδίων. Αν καταφέρουν να κάνουν γρήγορα, τα κουταβάκια της Μία σίγουρα θα κερδίσουν κάποιο βραβείο! Περιλαμβάνει την μίνι φιγούρα της Μία και 2 σκυλάκια.",
                            "title": "Καλλιστεία Σκύλων της Χάρτλεϊκ Σίτυ",
                            "tags": []
                        },
                        "en-us": {
                            "bullet_points": "• Includes Mia mini-doll figure and 2 puppies Scarlett and Jacky\r\n• Features podium with runway, grooming and preparation area, 2 obstacles, trophy with stand and outdoor scenery\r\n• Accessories include camera, bows, brushes, plate, bones, flowers, see saw, hurdle and flags\r\n• Win first prize with Mia's pretty puppies!\r\n• Wash and groom the puppies in the grooming area!\r\n• Impress the judges on the podium and runway!\r\n• Guide the puppies through the obstacle course!\r\n• LEGO® Friends pieces are fully compatible with all LEGO System bricks\r\n• Collect all of the LEGO Friends sets for a whole world of LEGO Friends fun!\r\n• LEGO mini-dolls are figures made especially for the world of LEGO Friends, with thousands of customizable fashion and accessory combinations!\r\n• Podium and runway measures over 5” (13cm) tall, 4” (12cm) wide and 4” (12cm) long\r\n• Grooming area measures over 1” (5cm) tall, 3” (9cm) wide and 1” (4cm) long",
                            "display_title": "Heartlake Dog Show",
                            "one_liner": "Guide Mia's puppies through the obstacle race in winning time at the Heartlake Dog Show with a Mia mini-doll figure and 2 puppies!",
                            "description": "It's a great day to be a pretty puppy in Heartlake City! Mia is taking her two puppies to the annual Heartlake Dog Show. Help her to show them on the podium and runway for the judges! Then, guide them through the obstacle race. If they can finish quickly, Mia's puppies are sure to win a prize! Includes Mia mini-doll figure and 2 puppies.",
